description.undefined: This ontology describes the tourist utilities of 11 spanish cities in order to help event planning and management. It has been produced as a practical assignment for the subject Knowledge Representation in Computer Science at Universitat Oberta de Catalunya.

abstract.value: This ontology has been created is part of an assignment in a Knowledge Representation course at Universitat Oberta de Catalunya. It has been developed with the main objective of learning the possibilities and structure of ontologies.
